entry.title: The Big Mistakes People Make in Medicare---And How to Avoid Them
entry.content: Seniors choosing Medicare plans can fall into traps leaving them with higher costs or fewer doctors than they expected. ‘I was so stupid.’

entry.title: Clashes Intensify as Israel Prepares Gaza Invasion
entry.content: Israeli jets carried out attacks against Lebanon-based militants, which include Iranian ally Hezbollah, after they launched at least six strikes against Israeli territory.

entry.title: Poland's Vote Provides Donald Tusk With Path Back to Power
entry.content: The ruling Law and Justice Party veered right to tap Ukraine fatigue, but failed to win enough votes to form a government.

entry.title: Egypt Weighs Letting In Palestinians From Gaza
entry.content: Cairo is coming under intense pressure to allow refugees to cross the border and escape an Israeli bombing campaign and expected ground invasion.
